_C_h_a_n_g_e_s _i_n _a_a_k_m_i_s_c _v_e_r_s_i_o_n _0._2_6:

        • The package no longer automatically loads ‘ggplot2’,
          ‘scales’, ‘grid’, ‘plyr’, ‘reshape2’, ‘magrittr’, and
          ‘readr’.

        • ‘scinot’ is now suitable for use in ‘ggplot::scale_X_Y’.

        • The new function ‘trnc’ allows truncation to the plot window
          when used in ‘ggplot::scale_X_Y’.

_C_h_a_n_g_e_s _i_n _a_a_k_m_i_s_c _v_e_r_s_i_o_n _0._2_5:

        • The license under which the software is provided has been
          upgraded to GPL version 3.

        • Package ‘readr’ is a new dependency and ‘scales’ is
          explicitly imported.

